            <li><a href="/dogs" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">/dogs</a> — Updated the "Puppy Development &amp; Temperament" accordion section. Replaced the old 4-card layout (Volhard PAT, Buyer Matching, Rearing Protocols, Documentation) with updated cards: Volhard PAT Testing, Gun Dog Aptitude Test, Working-Dog Role Suitability, and Rearing Protocols. Updated the feature grid card from "Volhard PAT, rearing protocols, buyer matching" to "Volhard PAT, Gun Dog Aptitude, working-dog suitability." Updated the temperament testing FAQ with details about all three assessment types.</li>
            <li><a href="/" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Homepage</a> — Renamed the "Rearing Protocols" feature card to "Rearing &amp; Temperament" with updated description mentioning Gun Dog Aptitude and working-dog role suitability. Updated the temperament testing FAQ answer. Expanded the structured data section from "Volhard PAT Temperament Testing" to "Temperament Testing Suite" covering all three assessment types, radar charts, sibling comparison, and buyer portal visibility.</li>
            <li><a href="/workflows" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">/workflows</a> — Renamed the "Rearing Protocols" card to "Rearing &amp; Temperament" with expanded description including Volhard PAT, Gun Dog Aptitude, working-dog suitability, radar charts, and buyer portal integration.</li>
          </ul>

