          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>Updated homepage structured data with comprehensive temperament testing suite description covering Volhard PAT, Gun Dog Aptitude Test, Working-Dog Role Suitability analysis, radar charts, sibling comparison, and buyer portal assessment visibility.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

